OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud soon lifting to
OL,6,Fleave a fine day. After a cool start,
OL,7,Fsoon feeling warm with plenty of
OL,8,Fstrong April sunshine despite a
OL,9,Fbreeze. Sunshine perhaps turning
OL,10,Fhazier later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome patchy cloud returning
OL,13,Fovernight leaving few clear spells.
OL,14,FTemperatures will fall away to low
OL,15,Fsingle figures with a couple frosty
OL,16,Fpatches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,169,160,301,260,100,100
