OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAfter early morning cloud
OL,6,Fclears, another bright and sunny day
OL,7,Fwill follow for all. Winds lighter
OL,8,Fthan Thursday allowing temperatures to
OL,9,Fclimb further. UV levels will also be
OL,10,Fhigh.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FStaying
OL,13,Fwarm and sunny into the weekend with
OL,14,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,15,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,16,Ftemperatures to dip slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
